{"tid":1033380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"芭蕾正妹張開雙腿　下體露出的東西太驚人","createTime":"2019-02-23T06:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T03:10:51.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ea9c9611e9b060c4c5d61ed84d21c2f1887b3a09","tid":1033380,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T06:20:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jBRjasvtSQg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjBRjasvtSQg&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1ITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=6734d358\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jBRjasvtSQg</a><br />\n一名來自烏克蘭來到俄羅斯學習芭蕾舞的正妹，近日拍攝了一段特技影片，這段影片到了後半段，嚇傻一堆網路鄉民。<br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報導，這名芭蕾正妹先跳起一段簡單的芭蕾舞步，隨後開始利用桿子，表演撐桿特技。過不久，正妹展開雙腿，這時她的下體，<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">竟然出現了一個「人臉」</span></span>，頓時間好似另一個女生在跳舞。<br />\n國外網友們紛紛表示：「太厲害了！」、「強大。」、「這是在做什麼性愛健身運動嗎...」、「男友看到會嚇死吧。」（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"ce237fc3a8c6a69e77f72b1a9da38a4d193dc0dd","tid":1033380,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T06:33:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e36d13b8a85f909e045e6a2291d4f8546fa6c6b4","tid":1033380,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T06:38:04.000Z","msg":"好cult<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1251f80333d783269cccc26c02ada4d1f24e198a","tid":1033380,"uid":916,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T06:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JNJ932R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJNJ932R.png&h=e1b5036b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67f95beb05bd9b7a5f9917d80cd3246c962e92c6","tid":1033380,"uid":69994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T08:55:58.000Z","msg